{"tid":2072137,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英華校長指辭職決定艱難    盼盡快與家人移居加拿大","createTime":"2020-06-20T11:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T11:34:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c63e88723413a48daa1767b1c0f7113577ca6554","tid":2072137,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/nJNebttIlTd71iuOhRZUyw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20200619a215505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FnJNebttIlTd71iuOhRZUyw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20200619a215505.jpg&h=e424fc23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/英華校長指辭職決定艱難-盼盡快與家人移居加國-140000742.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E8%8B%B1%E8%8F%AF%E6%A0%A1%E9%95%B7%E6%8C%87%E8%BE%AD%E8%81%B7%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E8%89%B1%E9%9B%A3-%E7%9B%BC%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E8%88%87%E5%AE%B6%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E5%B1%85%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B-140000742.html&d=KvAiISINul4H2q03UsPduWL0CtalYwMF7My3GtbBKd0%3D&h=a68768e0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/英華校長指辭職決定艱難-盼盡快與家人移居加國-140000742.html</a><br />\n<br />\n英華書院周一有學生在校園內高叫鼓吹港獨口號及反修例示威歌曲，受到社會批評。校長鄭鈞傑已向校方請辭，明年9月1日生效。<br />\n<br />\n鄭鈞傑向家長及學生發信，表示辭職是一個非常困難的決定，但過去將大部分把時間投放於英華書院的校務，認為現在是適合時間離任，期待盡快與海外的家人團聚。<br />\n<br />\n鄭鈞傑重申，離職的決定完全基於家庭需要，希望可以澄清近日有關辭職的揣測。鄭鈞傑又表示，辭職信已在上月提交，只是公布離任的時間，不幸發生了近日的事件。<br />\n<br />\n鄭鈞傑向傳媒透露，指去年4月已決定，未來會前往加拿大生活，妻兒會在今年暑假離港，自己則會留任至明年8月，之後才到加拿大家庭團聚。"},{"pid":"ffb661dd7548ad2509ca0bb06c375d8a0eed6fc9","tid":2072137,"uid":105526,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-20T11:16:15.000Z","msg":"走都走唔切"},{"pid":"1462f12bc0a40e181c678b1a24e2b3370080dbbc","tid":2072137,"uid":54959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"reply